        <h1>🔁 Return & Refund Policy</h1>
        <p>Effective as of March 11, 2025</p>
        <p>At <strong>FitHub Sdn Bhd</strong>, customer satisfaction is our priority. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you may be eligible for a return and refund. Please read our policy carefully.</p>

        <h2><strong>1. Conditions for Returns</strong></h2>
        <p>To be eligible for a return, the item must meet the following conditions:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ <strong>Return request must be made within 14 days</strong> from the delivery date</li>
            <li>✅ Item must be <strong>unused and in original condition</strong> (no signs of wear, damage, or alteration)</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Original packaging must be intact</strong> with all accessories included</li>
            <li>✅ <strong>Proof of purchase is required</strong> (order confirmation or receipt)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>🚨 <strong>Items that DO NOT meet these conditions will NOT be eligible for a return.</strong></p>

        <h2><strong>2. Refund & Exchange Policy</strong></h2>
        <p>We offer two options for eligible returns:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>🔄 <strong>Exchange</strong> – For defective or damaged items</li>
            <li>💰 <strong>Refund</strong> – Based on original payment method</li>
        </ul>

        <p>📌 <strong>Refund Processing Time:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Credit/Debit Cards</strong>: 5–10 business days</li>
            <li><strong>E-Wallet & Online Transfer</strong>: Within 5 business days</li>
            <li><strong>Cash Payments</strong>: via <strong>bank transfer</strong> or <strong>in-store refund</strong> (see Section 3)</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Exchange Process:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>1. Contact us at <strong>fithub888@gmail.com</strong> within <strong>7 days of receiving your order</strong></li>
            <li>2. Provide clear <strong>photos of the defect/damage</strong></li>
            <li>3. We will review and provide <strong>exchange approval & instructions</strong></li>
        </ul>
        <p>📦 <strong>Exchange items must be returned in original condition</strong></p>

        <h2><strong>3. Refund for Cash Payments</strong></h2>
        <p>For customers who paid with <strong>cash (Cash on Delivery or In-Store Purchases)</strong>, refunds are processed as follows:</p>

        <p>💰 <strong>Refund Methods:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>In-store Refund:</strong> Visit our store with receipt</li>
            <li><strong>Bank Transfer:</strong> Provide <strong>bank account for refund within 5–7 business days</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <p>🚨 <strong>Important:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>We do not provide <strong>cash refunds via courier.</strong></li>
            <li>Bank transfer refunds are only available to the <strong>original purchaser’s account.</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <h2><strong>4. Exchange Policy</strong></h2>
        <p>We only accept exchanges for <strong>defective or damaged items.</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>1. Contact us at <strong>fithub888@gmail.com</strong> within 7 days for receiving your order</li>
            <li>2. Provide clear photos of the damage</li>
            <li>3. We will review and provide exchange approval & shipping instructions</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Exchange items must be sent back in original condition</p>

        <h2><strong>5. Non-Refundable Items</strong></h2>
        <p>Certain items <strong>CANNOT be returned or refunded</strong>, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>🚫 Custom-made or personalized equipment</li>
            <li>🚫 Clearance or final sale items</li>
            <li>🚫 Hygiene-sensitive products (e.g., yoga mats, resistance bands)</li>
            <li>🚫 Gift cards and digital downloads</li>
        </ul>

        <h2><strong>6. How to Request a Return & Refund?</strong></h2>
        <p>📩 <strong>Step 1:</strong> Email us at <strong>fithub888@gmail.com</strong> with:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your order number</li>
            <li>The reason for return</li>
            <li>Photos (if defective)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>📦 <strong>Step 2:</strong> We will provide return instructions. You are responsible for <strong>return shipping costs</strong>, except in cases of wrong or defective items.</p>
        <p>💰 <strong>Step 3:</strong> Once received & inspected, we will <strong>process your refund</strong> within the timeframe stated in Section 2.</p>

        <h2><strong>7. Lost or Delayed Refunds</strong></h2>
        <ol>
            <li>1. Check your <strong>bank account or credit card statement</strong></li>
            <li>2. Contact your <strong>bank or payment provider</strong></li>
            <li>3. If you still have not received your refund after <strong>10 business days</strong>, contact us at <strong>fithub888@gmail.com</strong></li>
        </ol>

        <h2><strong>8. Changes to Return & Refund Policy</strong></h2>
        <p>We may update this policy at any time. <strong>Any changes will be posted on our website.</strong></p>
        <p>By purchasing from FitHub Sdn Bhd, you <strong>agree</strong> to our return & refund terms.</p>
        
